author: wn.com
title: Journalists Urge Republicans Not To Charge For Workspaces At 2016 Convention
text: Representatives for congressional journalists urged the Republican National Convention Committee on Monday to reconsider plans to charge reporters for workspaces at the 2016 Republican National Convention. The Northeast Ohio Media Group
